title: Jonathan Kodjia
snippet: November 2025, the 36-year-old remains unsigned to any club, with his future in professional football uncertain.[1] Born in France to Ivorian parents, Jonathan Kodjia was eligible to represent either France or Ivory Coast at the international level.
